OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,FA surge in frostbite cases so severe
OL,7,Fthey need hospital treatment has been
OL,8,Freported by doctors as temperatures
OL,9,Facross the country plummet.
OL,11,FMedics at the Midland Metropolitan
OL,12,FHospital in Smethwick say they have
OL,13,Fonly seen five or six cases in total
OL,14,Fover the past few years - and yet, so
OL,15,Ffar this winter, they have already had
OL,16,Fthree referrals.
OL,18,FMany of them, like Huibertjan
OL,19,FOmmering, are rough sleepers.
