OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,F"They have limited access to a warm
OL,7,Fenvironment, and also poor shoes and
OL,8,Fsocks too," surgeon Janak Bechar
OL,9,Fexplained.
OL,11,F"We generally see cases like this very
OL,12,Frarely in the UK - but his case
OL,13,Funfortunately is a bit more severe."
OL,15,FHuibertjan - known as 'Dutch' to his
OL,16,Ffriends - has been sleeping rough for
OL,17,Faround two months, after his
OL,18,Frelationship broke down and he had to
OL,19,Fleave his home.
