OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,FHe said he was managing to stay safe,
OL,7,Funtil temperatures plummeted.
OL,9,F"Horrible. Very horrible. You try to
OL,10,Fkeep yourself warm, with blankets if
OL,11,Fyou can find blankets, 20 layers of
OL,12,Fclothes on," he said.
OL,14,F"It's not nice."
OL,16,FBetween Christmas and New Year, things
OL,17,Fgot worse - and he realised something
OL,18,Fwas seriously wrong.
OL,20,FHe had developed severe frostbite on
OL,21,Fboth of his feet.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOUvD@PO]
