OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,FA friend called an ambulance for him,
OL,7,Fand now his feet - swollen and
OL,8,Fblackened - are bandaged up.
OL,10,FChances are that both will need to be
OL,11,Famputated.
OL,13,F"They're 99 per cent sure they will
OL,14,Fhave to take the feet off," he said.
OL,16,F"It's been very difficult.
OL,18,F"Today I'm alright, ish. But yesterday
OL,19,FI was crying because I'm going to lose
OL,20,Fmy feet.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@[O]xD@AOUzD@AOU
