OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,F"The last couple of days I've been
OL,7,Fcrying, then laughing. Just very
OL,8,Femotional."
OL,10,FAnd frostbite is just one of the
OL,11,Fissues facing staff at hospitals like
OL,12,Fthe Midland Met during times of
OL,13,Fextreme weather.
OL,15,FDeputy chief nurse Marsha Jones said
OL,16,Fplans have been put into place to help
OL,17,Fthem cope.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
