OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,F"It's really important to say that all
OL,7,Fservices are still running - emergency
OL,8,Fcare is still available to people,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"We have meetings right throughout the
OL,12,Fday with all key people in the
OL,13,Forganisation.
OL,15,F"One of the really important things is
OL,16,Fto make sure that we've got the
OL,17,Fstaffing resources - so we identify
OL,18,Fstaff that are able to get in safely,
OL,19,Fbut also identify those that is going
OL,20,Fto impact who are not able to get in.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@cO]sD@AOUwD@AOU
