OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F378A1767968719
OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,F"And we've worked really closely with
OL,7,Fthe senior nursing team to make sure
OL,8,Fwe've got additional staff who are
OL,9,Fclose to the hospital and who can
OL,10,Faccess the hospital safely and get
OL,11,Fhome safely as well."
OL,13,FThey're urging people to avoid going
OL,14,Fout unless they have to - and only go
OL,15,Fto A&E if it's an emergency.
OL,17,F"Pharmacy First is a great route," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]yD@AOUyD@bO]
