OL,3,CRough sleeper faces double amputation
OL,4,Cafter getting severe frostbite
OL,6,F"If you go onto the NHS website, it
OL,7,Fwill identify pharmacists that are
OL,8,Flocal to us and engaged in this, so
OL,9,Four pharmacists can offer support and
OL,10,Fguidance and advice.
OL,12,F"And our minor injuries units, as
OL,13,Fwell. Emergency department is for
OL,14,Femergency care. But as I say, our
OL,15,Fdoors are still open and will still
OL,16,Fprovide service for those patients
OL,17,Fthat need it."
OL,19,FAs for Huibertjan - his surgery is
OL,20,Flikely to be in the next couple of
OL,21,Fdays.
